ChangeList.Description: Added the [assign](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/intune-deviceConfiguration-assign?view=graph-rest-beta) method to the [deviceConfiguration](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/graph/api/resources/intune-deviceConfiguration?view=graph-rest-beta) resource.
